# Per-run outputs from offline regression harnesses (pass/fail
# tests, not trendy benchmarks). The harnesses still save a JSON
# locally for inspection, but committing every CI run's output
# just churns the repo. Commit harness outputs by hand when a run
# is worth archiving.
benchmarks/fit-analysis-*.json
benchmarks/manifest-build-*.json
benchmarks/orientation-corpus-*.json
